c: 5
v: 107
t: "Yoo isaan lamaan badii haqa godhachuun beekame, fira warra (dhaala) haqa godhate irraa namni lama bakka isaan lamaanii dhaabatanii \"ragaan keenya ragaa isaan lamaanii irra dhugaadha; nuti daangaas hin dabrine; yeroo san nuti miidhaa raawwattoota irraayyi\" (jedhanii) Rabbiin kakatu"